## Important Notes

- **Verified Domains Required**: Identifier URIs using `https://` must use a verified domain for your organization
- **api:// Format**: The `api://` format can use the application's client ID (app_id) and doesn't require domain verification
- **Multiple URIs**: You can add multiple identifier URIs to the same application by creating multiple instances of this resource
- **Uniqueness**: Each identifier URI must be unique across all applications in your tenant

